WEBVTT

1
00:00:14.083 --> 00:00:18.750
[man] Tell me.
are you being oppressed right now?

2
00:00:19.375 --> 00:00:23.625
Bullying at school. harassed at work.

3
00:00:24.208 --> 00:00:27.916
suffering unjust torment
that drives you to the edge?

4
00:00:28.708 --> 00:00:32.208
Do you want to become stronger?

5
00:00:33.583 --> 00:00:39.083
Become stronger.
and you can change your world.

6
00:00:41.125 --> 00:00:43.458
[birdsong]

7
00:00:45.583 --> 00:00:47.166
[alarm buzzing. ringing]

8
00:00:52.958 --> 00:00:54.041
[moans]

9
00:01:01.083 --> 00:01:02.208
[sneezes]

10
00:01:02.291 --> 00:01:04.750
BEWARE OF FRAUDULENT CHARGES!

11
00:01:06.458 --> 00:01:07.708
[sniffs]

12
00:01:09.250 --> 00:01:10.208
Mm.

13
00:01:12.458 --> 00:01:13.875
SAVE ELECTRICITY

14
00:01:22.375 --> 00:01:25.208
MOM

15
00:01:25.291 --> 00:01:27.500
[coins jangling]

16
00:01:33.375 --> 00:01:36.750
[mom] Good morning.
It's time for you to get going soon.

17
00:01:36.833 --> 00:01:38.666
Have fun at school today!

18
00:01:41.041 --> 00:01:43.291
THANKS. I WILL.

19
00:01:48.083 --> 00:01:49.208
SHIMURA

20
00:01:49.291 --> 00:01:52.000
[jaunty pop music playing]

21
00:01:52.083 --> 00:01:53.166
LIVE STREAM?

22
00:01:53.250 --> 00:01:54.208
AT LAST!

23
00:01:54.291 --> 00:01:55.125
WHEN?

24
00:01:55.208 --> 00:01:56.125
CAN'T WAIT!!!

25
00:01:56.625 --> 00:01:57.458
SO EXCITED!

26
00:01:57.541 --> 00:01:59.166
IS IT STARTING SOON?

27
00:01:59.250 --> 00:02:01.833
[messages popping]

28
00:02:03.375 --> 00:02:04.375
♪ Yo… ♪

29
00:02:04.458 --> 00:02:07.916
Allow me to introduce myself. I'm Hamaken.

30
00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:12.541
Today. we're celebrating reaching
more than 700.000 subscribers.

31
00:02:12.625 --> 00:02:16.625
And today you're going to meet someone
who's been trending wildly on Instagram.

32
00:02:16.708 --> 00:02:20.000
And here she is now.
the beautiful influencer Rumi. everyone!

33
00:02:20.083 --> 00:02:23.208
-[all cheering. whooping]
-Hi! Rumi. here.

34
00:02:23.291 --> 00:02:26.041
I'm just new to Instagram.
so if you could please like and subscribe.

35
00:02:26.125 --> 00:02:28.541
So. Rumi. what do you have
in store for us today?

36
00:02:28.625 --> 00:02:31.041
Yeah! Well. in today's makeup tutorial.

37
00:02:31.125 --> 00:02:33.750
we're going to give
a guy in my class a makeover!

38
00:02:33.833 --> 00:02:35.708
[all whooping]

39
00:02:35.791 --> 00:02:38.708
And right now.
I'll introduce today's model.

40
00:02:38.791 --> 00:02:40.125
[whispers] Just over here.

41
00:02:40.958 --> 00:02:43.125
-[girl 1] Huh?
-[girl 2] Yeah. I wonder who it is.

42
00:02:43.208 --> 00:02:45.416
-This is Shimura! Okay?
-[girl 2] Shimura?

43
00:02:45.500 --> 00:02:47.125
-Yay!
-[boy] Seriously?

44
00:02:47.208 --> 00:02:49.208
You're on camera. Smile for us.

45
00:02:49.291 --> 00:02:50.208
-And… cut!
-♪ Yo… ♪

46
00:02:50.291 --> 00:02:52.750
[rock music playing]

47
00:02:52.833 --> 00:02:54.166
Hey. Shimura.

48
00:02:54.250 --> 00:02:56.625
Try to look like you're having fun. okay?

49
00:02:56.708 --> 00:02:57.708
Sorry.

50
00:02:57.791 --> 00:02:59.875
It's worth 1.000 yen to you.

51
00:03:00.375 --> 00:03:01.708
You think this is a joke. huh?

52
00:03:01.791 --> 00:03:03.125
This punk thinks we're joking?

53
00:03:03.208 --> 00:03:05.750
-[boy 3] You messing with us?
-Hey. hold still.

54
00:03:07.541 --> 00:03:09.833
[students chattering. laughing]

55
00:03:09.916 --> 00:03:12.083
[Shimura] This is my "fun" school life.

56
00:03:12.791 --> 00:03:13.833
♪ Yo… ♪

57
00:03:13.916 --> 00:03:17.166
Hi. time to check out the big reveal!

58
00:03:17.666 --> 00:03:20.291
[students laughing]

59
00:03:20.375 --> 00:03:21.291
♪ Yo… ♪

60
00:03:23.833 --> 00:03:26.250
Come on. guys. This is too much.
Don't you think?

61
00:03:26.333 --> 00:03:27.708
What? You don't like it?

62
00:03:27.791 --> 00:03:31.083
Aw! Have we taken things too far? Have we?

63
00:03:31.166 --> 00:03:34.000
-[boy 4] This doesn't look cool.
-[Shimura] I laugh at things.

64
00:03:34.083 --> 00:03:36.750
I laugh at things
I don't find funny at all.

65
00:03:36.833 --> 00:03:39.750
Nod along to things I don't agree with.

66
00:03:40.458 --> 00:03:41.458
But I'm fine with it.

67
00:03:41.541 --> 00:03:44.291
-Those big black circles like a panda…
-This is how it is.

68
00:03:44.375 --> 00:03:47.958
Shimura! Say hello again
to all the viewers who are watching now.

69
00:03:48.916 --> 00:03:52.375
Hi. guys. I'm Kota Shimura.

70
00:03:52.958 --> 00:03:54.958
[students cheering mockingly]

71
00:03:55.041 --> 00:03:56.500
[tense music playing]

72
00:03:56.583 --> 00:03:58.125
And I just take it.

73
00:04:00.791 --> 00:04:02.375
[music swells. then fades]

74
00:04:04.166 --> 00:04:06.583
I can't get it off.

75
00:04:07.791 --> 00:04:10.041
[Shimura] What do I have to offer anyway?

76
00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.125
He may suck at studying.
but he's got a talent

77
00:04:13.208 --> 00:04:14.708
for making money through streaming.

78
00:04:14.791 --> 00:04:17.125
Hey. we've made 50.000 yen already.

79
00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.541
-Whoa!
-[Rumi] Oh? Oh.

80
00:04:19.625 --> 00:04:22.208
-Hey. hey. hey. Hamaken.
-Hamaken's amazing. no doubt.

81
00:04:22.291 --> 00:04:24.791
[Shimura] She has the talent to get by
with her good looks alone.

82
00:04:24.875 --> 00:04:26.958
That's all right. You can have his share.

83
00:04:27.041 --> 00:04:28.583
-Huh?!
-Yeah?

84
00:04:28.666 --> 00:04:31.000
Oh. yeah. Sure. It's yours.

85
00:04:31.083 --> 00:04:32.708
-Ah. thank you!
-Sure.

86
00:04:32.791 --> 00:04:36.208
[Shimura] And this guy knows how to
brownnose his way up the social ladder.

87
00:04:37.666 --> 00:04:40.416
But me? I have nothing.

88
00:04:41.375 --> 00:04:44.500
I'm at the very bottom
of the school's social ladder.

89
00:04:45.166 --> 00:04:46.583
-[coin jangles]
-Oh!

90
00:04:52.166 --> 00:04:55.250
Look at you.
Desperate for a measly 10 yen. hey?

91
00:04:55.333 --> 00:04:56.958
I guess being poor sucks!

92
00:04:57.041 --> 00:04:58.083
[Hamaken and Rumi laugh]

93
00:04:58.166 --> 00:05:00.541
[ominous music playing]

94
00:05:00.625 --> 00:05:03.208
Uh… um. where's my 1.000 yen?

95
00:05:03.291 --> 00:05:04.166
What?

96
00:05:04.791 --> 00:05:07.875
You said I'd get
a thousand yen for the makeover.

97
00:05:07.958 --> 00:05:09.333
Did I say that? Really?

98
00:05:09.416 --> 00:05:10.875
[Yumi laughs] I don't remember.

99
00:05:10.958 --> 00:05:12.750
[singsong] I don't recall that!

100
00:05:12.833 --> 00:05:13.666
[all laugh]

101
00:05:13.750 --> 00:05:15.791
-But I only agreed because you--
-[grunts]

102
00:05:15.875 --> 00:05:17.625
[groaning] Ugh!

103
00:05:17.708 --> 00:05:19.458
-[wincing] Agh!
-[Hamaken] Shut up. loser.

104
00:05:19.541 --> 00:05:22.375
Just a thousand yen. Why so desperate?

105
00:05:22.458 --> 00:05:23.750
Oh. I know.

106
00:05:24.208 --> 00:05:27.875
It's your mom. isn't it?
She's still alive. is she?

107
00:05:28.541 --> 00:05:32.500
Oh. I forgot she's sick!
Oh! That's why you're so poor!

108
00:05:32.583 --> 00:05:34.208
-Is that what it is?
-[all laughing]

109
00:05:34.291 --> 00:05:36.041
-[boy 1] Hey!
-[Hamaken] Hey. let's go.

110
00:05:36.125 --> 00:05:38.458
[boy 2 laughs] That was so mean!

111
00:05:38.541 --> 00:05:40.541
[boy 1] Yeah. He'll do anything for money.

112
00:05:52.666 --> 00:05:53.833
[Shimura] I should have…

113
00:05:56.875 --> 00:06:00.166
I should have taken a swing at them
and fought back.

114
00:06:01.291 --> 00:06:03.041
-[sniffles]
-[music fades]

115
00:06:03.125 --> 00:06:05.416
URABE GENERAL HOSPITAL

116
00:06:05.500 --> 00:06:07.791
-[mom] What happened to your face?
-Huh?

117
00:06:07.875 --> 00:06:10.083
Oh. you weren't fighting
with anyone. were you?

118
00:06:10.750 --> 00:06:13.250
No. I would never do that.

119
00:06:13.333 --> 00:06:16.166
-I just tripped. that's all.
-Really? That's okay then.

120
00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:18.250
I got you a rice cake. [giggles]

121
00:06:21.625 --> 00:06:23.875
TOTAL AMOUNT DUE: 3.140.000 YEN

122
00:06:23.958 --> 00:06:25.125
How's school going?

123
00:06:25.208 --> 00:06:27.125
[poignant music playing]

124
00:06:27.208 --> 00:06:29.250
Mm. It's okay. [chuckles]

125
00:06:29.791 --> 00:06:32.333
Good. Well. don't worry about me.

126
00:06:32.416 --> 00:06:34.791
Just enjoy your high school life.

127
00:06:35.791 --> 00:06:37.541
'Cause you are…

128
00:06:38.708 --> 00:06:40.250
only young once.

129
00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:46.833
AMERICAN HOUSE DINER

130
00:06:46.916 --> 00:06:48.708
[rock music playing over speakers]

131
00:06:53.291 --> 00:06:55.583
-[fryer sizzling]
-[Shimura] This is my youth.

132
00:06:56.208 --> 00:06:58.375
I spend my days frying potatoes here.

133
00:06:58.458 --> 00:07:00.375
[man] Shimura. hurry up with order 60.

134
00:07:00.458 --> 00:07:01.291
Uh. yes. sir.

135
00:07:03.916 --> 00:07:04.791
Here.

136
00:07:04.875 --> 00:07:08.208
My life is… so shit.

137
00:07:09.375 --> 00:07:11.416
Can I have everyone's attention. please?

138
00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:13.666
Please. say hello to our newest employee.

139
00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:16.333
Oh man. like we're not slammed.

140
00:07:17.958 --> 00:07:18.958
Nice to meet you.

141
00:07:19.041 --> 00:07:22.083
[bubbly romantic music playing]

142
00:07:22.166 --> 00:07:24.208
I'm Kaho Asamiya.

143
00:07:25.375 --> 00:07:28.083
Okay. maybe it's not so shit.

144
00:07:28.166 --> 00:07:29.583
Nice to be working here.

145
00:07:29.666 --> 00:07:31.583
If you have any questions.
just ask any of us.

146
00:07:31.666 --> 00:07:32.750
[Kaho] I will.

147
00:07:34.166 --> 00:07:35.375
[timer beeping]

148
00:07:35.458 --> 00:07:37.416
-Ah! It's hot!
-[sizzling]

149
00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:41.083
Crap! I stared too long.
She must think that I'm a creep.

150
00:07:43.166 --> 00:07:44.791
-Bacon cheeseburger combo.
-Yes!

151
00:07:44.875 --> 00:07:46.375
[Kaho] Great. coming right up.

152
00:07:47.541 --> 00:07:49.500
Shimura. what are you doing?
You've got an order.

153
00:07:49.583 --> 00:07:50.750
Yes. sir.5

154
00:07:50.833 --> 00:07:51.750
[entry bell jingles]

155
00:07:51.833 --> 00:07:54.083
Hello. everyone!
I'm Hamaken. the streamer.

156
00:07:54.166 --> 00:07:57.416
-Hamaken? What are they doing here?
-With 700.000 subscribers.

157
00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:59.500
-[Hamaken] Streaming from a burger joint.
-Oh. crap.

158
00:07:59.583 --> 00:08:01.333
[boy 1] Hey. hey. hey. guys!

159
00:08:01.416 --> 00:08:03.833
All right. here's today's mission
from our viewers.

160
00:08:03.916 --> 00:08:04.750
Ta-da!

161
00:08:04.833 --> 00:08:07.875
Can they make a cheeseburger
like this one in under 30 seconds?!

162
00:08:07.958 --> 00:08:09.125
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

163
00:08:09.208 --> 00:08:11.625
And if they fail this important challenge.

164
00:08:11.708 --> 00:08:15.875
then. uh… this cute little waitress
has no choice but to give us her number.

165
00:08:15.958 --> 00:08:19.500
You're bothering the other customers.
I think you should stop doing this.

166
00:08:19.583 --> 00:08:22.791
I apologize. I'm not all for it either.
but it's my viewers.

167
00:08:22.875 --> 00:08:24.083
They keep egging me on.

168
00:08:24.166 --> 00:08:25.875
-Thanks for your cooperation!
-Thank you!

169
00:08:25.958 --> 00:08:28.875
-I'm sorry. we can't do this.
-Okay. start the clock!

170
00:08:28.958 --> 00:08:29.833
-Huh?
-One.

171
00:08:29.916 --> 00:08:32.875
-[Kaho] Wait.
-[Hamaken. boys] Two. three. four. five.

172
00:08:32.958 --> 00:08:36.041
-Six. seven. eight. nine. ten.…
-What should we do about this?

173
00:08:36.125 --> 00:08:37.416
Uh. what do you mean "we"?

174
00:08:37.500 --> 00:08:39.125
-Where's the boss?
-He stepped out.

175
00:08:39.208 --> 00:08:41.541
They're banned
from filming here without access.

176
00:08:41.625 --> 00:08:42.500
-Stop them.
-Me?!

177
00:08:42.583 --> 00:08:44.750
-[boys] …21. 22. 23. 24…
-Oh. okay.

178
00:08:44.833 --> 00:08:47.916
-…25. 26. 27. 28…
-Sir. the manager. he's not here just now.

179
00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.166
Sorry for the wait.
Here's your Monster Cheeseburger.

180
00:08:54.666 --> 00:08:56.041
You…

181
00:08:58.791 --> 00:09:00.750
-[Hamaken] Let's go.
-[boy 1] Let's get outta here.

182
00:09:02.041 --> 00:09:05.916
-[music playing faintly over speakers]
-[entry bell jingles]

183
00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:07.208
Didn't see me.

184
00:09:07.291 --> 00:09:09.291
[sighs] Oh. thank goodness.

185
00:09:10.250 --> 00:09:11.916
[sighs deeply]

186
00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:13.958
Oh. thank you. Shimura.

187
00:09:14.833 --> 00:09:17.041
Uh… uh. how do you know my name?

188
00:09:17.916 --> 00:09:18.750
[laughs] That.

189
00:09:18.833 --> 00:09:20.458
SHIMURA

190
00:09:20.541 --> 00:09:22.541
Yeah. Uh. of course.

191
00:09:22.625 --> 00:09:24.875
[Shimura] Oh. crap.
I'm being creepy again.

192
00:09:24.958 --> 00:09:26.041
[giggles]

193
00:09:29.708 --> 00:09:30.583
But…

194
00:09:30.666 --> 00:09:31.708
I'm terribly sorry.

195
00:09:31.791 --> 00:09:34.250
-She thanked me.
-Terribly sorry.

196
00:09:34.833 --> 00:09:36.708
So sorry for all the trouble.

197
00:09:37.708 --> 00:09:39.083
Please enjoy your meals.

198
00:09:39.166 --> 00:09:41.208
[humming]

199
00:09:41.291 --> 00:09:43.416
[gasps] She said. "Thank you."

200
00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:47.041
[continues humming]

201
00:09:47.125 --> 00:09:48.916
It's Shimura.

202
00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.000
[tense music playing]

203
00:09:50.083 --> 00:09:52.416
Bastard. Why'd you get in my way?

204
00:09:53.041 --> 00:09:53.875
-Huh?
-[groans]

205
00:09:53.958 --> 00:09:56.750
-[whimpering]
-Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh?

206
00:09:56.833 --> 00:09:58.083
-[blows thudding]
-[yelps] Oh!

207
00:09:58.166 --> 00:09:59.833
-Huh?
-I'm sorry.

208
00:09:59.916 --> 00:10:01.958
Sorry isn't gonna cut it.

209
00:10:02.541 --> 00:10:03.541
[grunts]

210
00:10:04.625 --> 00:10:08.666
Hey. you ruined my content. you did.

211
00:10:08.750 --> 00:10:09.958
"Your" content?

212
00:10:10.875 --> 00:10:14.416
Don't you dare interfere
with Hamaken's content?

213
00:10:14.500 --> 00:10:16.375
-[kick thuds]
-[Kaho] Shimura?

214
00:10:17.250 --> 00:10:18.500
[Hamaken] Hey! Are you okay?

215
00:10:18.583 --> 00:10:20.583
-[laughing]
-[Hamaken] Careful. Let me help you.

216
00:10:20.666 --> 00:10:22.333
-There.
-Shimura.

217
00:10:22.416 --> 00:10:23.791
[Hamaken] Well. then.

218
00:10:23.875 --> 00:10:26.041
Good luck with work.

219
00:10:26.125 --> 00:10:27.041
[Shimura gulps]

220
00:10:29.750 --> 00:10:31.708
-[whimpers]
-Enjoy your shift.

221
00:10:33.666 --> 00:10:35.083
[door closes]

222
00:10:35.166 --> 00:10:36.708
Hey. you okay?

223
00:10:36.791 --> 00:10:38.166
[Shimura] Uh. sure.

224
00:10:39.333 --> 00:10:41.333
Uh… oh. them there?

225
00:10:41.416 --> 00:10:44.208
No. it's nothing at all. really.
I just fell. That's all.

226
00:10:44.875 --> 00:10:47.125
Uh. those guys. they're in my class.

227
00:10:47.208 --> 00:10:48.375
We're friends.

228
00:10:50.125 --> 00:10:54.375
Lame. It's so obvious we're not friends.

229
00:10:54.458 --> 00:10:55.541
[door opens]

230
00:10:55.625 --> 00:10:56.791
[phone buzzes]

231
00:10:56.875 --> 00:10:58.041
[door closes]

232
00:10:59.416 --> 00:11:01.500
WHAT TIME WILL YOU BE HOME TODAY?

233
00:11:04.083 --> 00:11:06.458
I HAVE SELF-STUDY. I'LL BE LATE.

234
00:11:10.958 --> 00:11:13.208
[game controller tapping]

235
00:11:16.666 --> 00:11:19.000
[video game explosions]

236
00:11:22.416 --> 00:11:24.625
[Yumi] Huh? What's your problem?

237
00:11:24.708 --> 00:11:28.500
I don't have a problem.
This seat here is mine. So. please move.

238
00:11:28.583 --> 00:11:31.375
[girl 1] She's so full of herself.

239
00:11:32.833 --> 00:11:35.958
-You're coming with me.
-Let me go! [grunts]

240
00:11:36.041 --> 00:11:37.333
[gasps]

241
00:11:38.916 --> 00:11:42.083
[tense music playing]

242
00:11:48.458 --> 00:11:49.791
[game creature screeches]

243
00:11:51.375 --> 00:11:55.083
-What a rough morning.
-Hey. little girl boss is strong.

244
00:11:55.166 --> 00:11:56.458
[Yumi] You're doing so well.

245
00:11:56.541 --> 00:11:58.291
[girl 2] Oh. I wonder who did it.

246
00:12:02.583 --> 00:12:05.000
-You piss me off.
-[girl 1] Oh. yeah.

247
00:12:05.083 --> 00:12:06.666
[girl 1] Gloomy-ass bitch.

248
00:12:07.291 --> 00:12:09.666
[girls laughing]

249
00:12:15.166 --> 00:12:17.166
SCHOOL MOTTO
LET YOUR DREAMS SHINE

250
00:12:23.541 --> 00:12:26.125
[music intensifies]

251
00:12:30.291 --> 00:12:31.125
[music fades]

252
00:12:31.916 --> 00:12:33.750
MISSION FAILED

253
00:12:35.750 --> 00:12:37.083
[game controller clatters]

254
00:12:41.916 --> 00:12:44.500
-[raucous dance music playing]
-[all] Oh!

255
00:12:52.333 --> 00:12:54.250
[all cheering] Yeah!

256
00:12:56.416 --> 00:12:59.541
Bottoms up. Have some more. Here you go.

257
00:13:00.833 --> 00:13:02.333
[girl 1] Whoa! Cocky bitch.

258
00:13:02.416 --> 00:13:05.000
Hey! Was this really just for content?

259
00:13:05.083 --> 00:13:06.041
Hmm?

260
00:13:06.125 --> 00:13:07.750
[Yumi] You weren't trying
to get a number?

261
00:13:07.833 --> 00:13:08.666
DESPERATE FOR HER NUMBER

262
00:13:08.750 --> 00:13:10.333
Of course not.

263
00:13:11.833 --> 00:13:13.875
Hmm. That's what I thought.

264
00:13:15.208 --> 00:13:18.125
[sighs] I don't want you texting
other girls. okay?

265
00:13:18.208 --> 00:13:21.291
Dummy. You're the only one for me.

266
00:13:23.916 --> 00:13:26.833
-[music stops]
-[snack back crinkles]

267
00:13:26.916 --> 00:13:28.000
DANDAN NOODLES

268
00:13:28.083 --> 00:13:30.750
[boy] Whoa! Too close! Too close! Whoa!

269
00:13:32.416 --> 00:13:34.666
-Hell yeah!
-[Shimura] Why is this happening?

270
00:13:34.750 --> 00:13:38.375
[boy] Ah! Too bad.
Thanks for your 3.000 yen donation!

271
00:13:39.791 --> 00:13:44.375
What? Complete the next hunt
in under three minutes for 30.000 yen?

272
00:13:44.458 --> 00:13:47.291
Are you sure?
That's a piece of cake for me.

273
00:13:47.875 --> 00:13:48.708
[laughs]

274
00:13:48.791 --> 00:13:49.625
[mouthing]

275
00:13:49.708 --> 00:13:51.791
Uh. sorry. almost done.

276
00:13:53.625 --> 00:13:58.250
All the viewers saying I can't do it.
If I succeed. you'd better donate a lot.

277
00:13:58.958 --> 00:14:00.291
All right. here I go.

278
00:14:00.958 --> 00:14:01.791
Very nice.

279
00:14:01.875 --> 00:14:03.833
-Why?
-[boy] All right. All right.

280
00:14:03.916 --> 00:14:06.000
Why did I let him into my house?

281
00:14:11.125 --> 00:14:14.625
I figured I'd open my own channel
and rake in all the donations.

282
00:14:16.416 --> 00:14:17.666
But you know what?

283
00:14:18.166 --> 00:14:20.291
It's hard for minors to open a channel.

284
00:14:20.375 --> 00:14:23.375
You need your parent's bank account
and other stuff like that.

285
00:14:24.041 --> 00:14:27.416
-Ah. I see.
-Your mom's in hospital. Isn't that right?

286
00:14:28.666 --> 00:14:30.666
Mm. Ah! [gasping]

287
00:14:30.750 --> 00:14:32.583
You know what I mean?

288
00:14:33.083 --> 00:14:37.708
[Shimura] He's making money using
my mom's ID and bank account details.

289
00:14:37.791 --> 00:14:38.875
[boy] Oh. here we go!

290
00:14:38.958 --> 00:14:40.666
[Shimura] Mom. I'm really sorry.

291
00:14:40.750 --> 00:14:42.250
[boy] Yes! Yes. yes!

292
00:14:42.333 --> 00:14:46.375
Oh. I'm so close
to the 30.000 yen! Yes! Oh!

293
00:14:46.458 --> 00:14:48.375
One last hit! Here we go!

294
00:14:48.458 --> 00:14:51.916
Three. two. one…

295
00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:54.375
-[loud click echoes]
-[electricity crackles]

296
00:14:54.458 --> 00:14:56.416
-[low bass rumbles]
-[no audible dialogue]

297
00:15:04.958 --> 00:15:07.333
-[screams] Ah! It's hot! Ah! Ah!
-[rock music playing]

298
00:15:07.416 --> 00:15:09.583
Oh! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

299
00:15:09.666 --> 00:15:11.416
[gasping. whimpering]

300
00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:14.333
[gasping]

301
00:15:15.541 --> 00:15:16.625
[huffs]

302
00:15:17.250 --> 00:15:20.000
-What the hell have you done?
-Ah!

303
00:15:20.833 --> 00:15:22.000
-[whimpering]
-[grunting]

304
00:15:22.083 --> 00:15:23.500
I said I'm sorry!

305
00:15:23.583 --> 00:15:26.250
-I was one strike away from 30.000 yen!
-I'm sorry!

306
00:15:26.333 --> 00:15:28.541
How are you gonna make up for this?!
You'd better pay up!

307
00:15:28.625 --> 00:15:31.375
-[whimpering]
-That's right! You owe me now!

308
00:15:31.458 --> 00:15:33.583
[Shimura] I can't
just come up with 30.000 yen!

309
00:15:33.666 --> 00:15:34.833
[clattering]

310
00:15:34.916 --> 00:15:37.666
-Don't run away. you bastard!
-[screaming]

311
00:15:37.750 --> 00:15:39.833
[Shimura gasping]

312
00:15:39.916 --> 00:15:42.500
You're too poor. aren't you? [snarls]

313
00:15:42.583 --> 00:15:44.000
[Shimura gasping] Ow!

314
00:15:44.916 --> 00:15:45.791
[yells] Ah!

315
00:15:45.875 --> 00:15:47.833
[panting]

316
00:15:47.916 --> 00:15:48.791
[tapping keyboard]

317
00:15:48.875 --> 00:15:50.000
[Shimura] How pathetic.

318
00:15:50.083 --> 00:15:52.833
Why do I have to get beaten up
in my own home?

319
00:15:52.916 --> 00:15:54.916
Ah. damn it! Damn it!

320
00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:58.833
You're a useless piece of shit!

321
00:15:58.916 --> 00:16:01.250
-[grunting]
-[yelping]

322
00:16:01.333 --> 00:16:02.958
-[boy snarling]
-[Shimura grunts]

323
00:16:03.750 --> 00:16:04.625
[whimpers]

324
00:16:04.708 --> 00:16:08.958
Your mom is gonna die
because you're useless shit!

325
00:16:09.041 --> 00:16:10.833
[tense music playing]

326
00:16:10.916 --> 00:16:12.375
[laughs]

327
00:16:17.708 --> 00:16:20.041
[Shimura straining]

328
00:16:25.083 --> 00:16:27.541
What are you holding onto me for?

329
00:16:27.625 --> 00:16:29.833
What the hell are you doing? Let me go!

330
00:16:29.916 --> 00:16:31.583
[straining]

331
00:16:31.666 --> 00:16:33.166
[grunting]

332
00:16:33.250 --> 00:16:34.833
[roaring]

333
00:16:37.791 --> 00:16:40.041
[Shimura] The first fist I ever raised.

334
00:16:40.125 --> 00:16:42.083
The first person I ever hit.

335
00:16:42.166 --> 00:16:43.541
-[yells] Ah!
-[boy groans]

336
00:16:43.625 --> 00:16:46.583
[boy] Stop it! The hell's wrong with you?

337
00:16:48.333 --> 00:16:51.083
[Shimura] And the first fist in my face.

338
00:16:52.208 --> 00:16:53.333
You've got some nerve!

339
00:16:53.416 --> 00:16:54.625
[Shimura roars]

340
00:16:56.041 --> 00:16:57.250
[grunting]

341
00:16:57.333 --> 00:16:58.166
[voices muted]

342
00:16:58.250 --> 00:17:03.041
[Shimura] Fighting turned out...
to not be as big a deal as I thought.

343
00:17:15.458 --> 00:17:17.625
Ah! It's… sore.

344
00:17:20.541 --> 00:17:21.416
[sighs]

345
00:17:26.333 --> 00:17:27.916
What a mess.

346
00:17:29.208 --> 00:17:30.958
I've gotta clean.

347
00:17:32.083 --> 00:17:34.583
[groaning]

348
00:17:36.500 --> 00:17:37.875
Ah! Gotta save power.

349
00:17:40.500 --> 00:17:42.125
[sighs]

350
00:18:04.875 --> 00:18:06.416
Immunotherapy?

351
00:18:06.500 --> 00:18:07.541
[man] That's correct.

352
00:18:08.041 --> 00:18:11.041
Keytruda is a very promising drug.

353
00:18:11.125 --> 00:18:14.541
I suggested it to your mother.
but she declined.

354
00:18:17.125 --> 00:18:19.958
[woman] Your mother always brags
about you. Shimura.

355
00:18:20.583 --> 00:18:24.083
She says you're a sweet boy
who's never gotten in a fight.

356
00:18:29.916 --> 00:18:31.500
Let me think about this.

357
00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:33.458
[man] Yes. of course.

358
00:18:36.291 --> 00:18:39.458
[train clacking]

359
00:18:40.041 --> 00:18:41.291
[Shimura] That's what I said.

360
00:18:42.375 --> 00:18:43.625
But what am I gonna do?

361
00:18:43.708 --> 00:18:47.958
[phone ringing]

362
00:18:49.166 --> 00:18:50.125
[ringing stops]

363
00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:52.083
Hello?

364
00:18:52.166 --> 00:18:53.708
[boy] Where the hell are you?

365
00:18:53.791 --> 00:18:54.625
What?

366
00:18:54.708 --> 00:18:57.250
-[suspenseful music playing]
-The video! Delete it!

367
00:18:57.750 --> 00:18:58.708
What video?

368
00:18:58.791 --> 00:19:03.041
The live stream from yesterday.
it's been uploaded!

369
00:19:03.125 --> 00:19:05.458
Huh? Oh. Well. I… I…

370
00:19:05.541 --> 00:19:07.333
But… I thought I pulled the plug out.

371
00:19:09.375 --> 00:19:11.125
Was that the monitor's power?

372
00:19:11.208 --> 00:19:12.750
So the computer was still on?

373
00:19:12.833 --> 00:19:14.416
The whole fight! The whole goddamn thing!

374
00:19:14.500 --> 00:19:18.500
Now everyone can see everything!
It was all streamed from the webcam.

375
00:19:18.833 --> 00:19:19.916
LIVE FIGHT LOL

376
00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:21.416
BOTH OF THEM SUCK

377
00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:22.833
I'M CRYING! ROFLMAO

378
00:19:26.166 --> 00:19:28.791
[Shimura] It's got over 100.000 views.

379
00:19:29.375 --> 00:19:31.750
Well. wait a minute. I never uploaded it.

380
00:19:31.833 --> 00:19:34.750
Then you must have
turned off the computer.

381
00:19:34.833 --> 00:19:37.166
[Shimura] Ah! Gotta save power.

382
00:19:38.791 --> 00:19:39.666
Oh.

383
00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:43.708
The video automatically uploads
when the computer is turned off midstream!

384
00:19:43.791 --> 00:19:45.500
[music winds down]

385
00:19:46.166 --> 00:19:48.500
[suspenseful music playing]

386
00:19:55.250 --> 00:19:57.291
[huffing]

387
00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:04.208
KANEGON'S GAME STREAM. 130K VIEWS

388
00:20:04.291 --> 00:20:06.583
What do I do? How do I delete it?

389
00:20:12.666 --> 00:20:14.083
NO VIDEOS UPLOADED

390
00:20:14.166 --> 00:20:15.125
[exhales]

391
00:20:16.500 --> 00:20:18.791
-[gasping]
-[music ends]

392
00:20:20.125 --> 00:20:22.625
HIGH SCHOOL

393
00:20:23.958 --> 00:20:27.916
-[indistinct chatter]
-[Shimura] I really hope nobody's seen it.

394
00:20:35.041 --> 00:20:36.916
Looks like I'm in the clear.

395
00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:46.291
Mr. Viral Streamer! Oh. hey there!

396
00:20:46.375 --> 00:20:47.750
-[boy 1] Hey!
-[boy 2] Morning!

397
00:20:47.833 --> 00:20:49.041
It's gone viral!

398
00:20:49.125 --> 00:20:50.458
[Hamaken] Shimura.

399
00:20:50.541 --> 00:20:53.208
Why didn't you tell us
that you'd started streaming?

400
00:20:53.291 --> 00:20:54.166
[laughter]

401
00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:57.958
-Well. that was…
-Oh. come on. Hamaken. Knock it off.

402
00:20:58.041 --> 00:21:01.208
-Must be super embarrassing. right?
-[laughs]

403
00:21:01.291 --> 00:21:04.916
Isn't this really crazy though?
People overseas are watching it too.

404
00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:07.291
-[laughter]
-[Shimura] How did it come to this?

405
00:21:07.375 --> 00:21:08.666
[boy 3] Shimura!

406
00:21:11.833 --> 00:21:14.000
You little…

407
00:21:14.791 --> 00:21:18.333
[grunts] Agh! Agh!

408
00:21:18.416 --> 00:21:19.583
Huh?

409
00:21:20.750 --> 00:21:22.791
Know what? You're a puny ass.

410
00:21:23.458 --> 00:21:24.333
Hamaken?

411
00:21:24.416 --> 00:21:26.208
Don't talk to me like a friend.

412
00:21:27.583 --> 00:21:29.416
Hey. stop joking around.

413
00:21:29.500 --> 00:21:33.458
I've come up with a new idea.
It'll make your channel even greater.

414
00:21:33.541 --> 00:21:34.416
Not interested.

415
00:21:35.541 --> 00:21:38.250
How could you lose
to a piece of trash like that?

416
00:21:40.708 --> 00:21:42.625
Oh. don't talk like that.

417
00:21:42.708 --> 00:21:45.333
-Aren't we friends? You know?
-You think?

418
00:21:45.416 --> 00:21:46.666
[laughing]

419
00:21:46.750 --> 00:21:49.875
-Give me a goddamn break.
-[continues laughing] Ho ho ho!

420
00:21:49.958 --> 00:21:52.708
You think I'm friends
with a loser like this?

421
00:21:53.416 --> 00:21:55.541
-[boy 1 laughing]
-[boy 2] Whoa!

422
00:21:55.625 --> 00:21:57.125
[boy 4] Hell no!

423
00:21:57.208 --> 00:21:58.541
[all laughing]

424
00:21:59.125 --> 00:22:02.875
[girl 1 laughing] Oh my God.
they're perfect for each other!

425
00:22:02.958 --> 00:22:04.416
Shit!

426
00:22:07.125 --> 00:22:08.875
-[boy sobs]
-[Shimura] Are you okay?

427
00:22:08.958 --> 00:22:10.041
You shut up!

428
00:22:10.541 --> 00:22:14.166
You're the lucky one.
You've got nothing to lose.

429
00:22:15.916 --> 00:22:20.375
[sobs] I worked so hard
to get into Hamaken's good books.

430
00:22:21.500 --> 00:22:23.708
-What will you do?
-What will I do?!

431
00:22:23.791 --> 00:22:25.125
You asshole!

432
00:22:25.708 --> 00:22:28.500
I'm not going down like this. [sobs]

433
00:22:29.541 --> 00:22:31.208
I'm going to climb back up!

434
00:22:34.500 --> 00:22:35.833
What about yo?

435
00:22:36.333 --> 00:22:37.625
Are you okay with this?

436
00:22:38.375 --> 00:22:39.208
Huh?

437
00:22:39.291 --> 00:22:42.333
Are you okay being at the bottom
of the school's hierarchy?

438
00:22:43.916 --> 00:22:44.958
[mom] You are

439
00:22:45.541 --> 00:22:47.083
only young once.

440
00:22:47.166 --> 00:22:50.416
[boy] Are you okay being
everyone's laughingstock?

441
00:22:52.083 --> 00:22:53.750
[poignant music playing softly]

442
00:22:53.833 --> 00:22:55.833
Hmm. Doesn't bother me.

443
00:22:55.916 --> 00:22:57.500
I've come to terms with it.

444
00:22:58.416 --> 00:23:00.166
Come to terms with it?

445
00:23:01.750 --> 00:23:04.083
Besides. what can I do
to change at this point?

446
00:23:16.583 --> 00:23:18.458
BARBER YASHIO

447
00:23:25.750 --> 00:23:27.625
Whoa-ho-ho. It's freezing.

448
00:23:27.708 --> 00:23:29.958
[boys grunting on video]

449
00:23:37.875 --> 00:23:40.125
[dad] Aki. dinner's ready!

450
00:23:40.875 --> 00:23:41.791
[clicks]

451
00:23:46.416 --> 00:23:47.250
[dad] Mm.

452
00:23:49.375 --> 00:23:50.250
Mm.

453
00:23:50.750 --> 00:23:51.625
Hmm?

454
00:23:52.875 --> 00:23:55.791
Did something… good happen?

455
00:23:55.875 --> 00:23:56.916
No. not really.

456
00:23:58.375 --> 00:23:59.333
Okay.

457
00:24:00.875 --> 00:24:01.875
Mm.

458
00:24:03.291 --> 00:24:04.375
Mm-hmm.

459
00:24:07.833 --> 00:24:10.166
I'm so astonished to hear

460
00:24:10.250 --> 00:24:13.625
those two everyone's been talking about
are in my class at school.

461
00:24:13.708 --> 00:24:15.416
[astonished voices] Eh?

462
00:24:15.500 --> 00:24:16.875
What? Make them fight?

463
00:24:16.958 --> 00:24:20.041
I can't do that
because they're very good friends of mine.

464
00:24:20.125 --> 00:24:21.458
[boy 1] Oh. yeah. sure.

465
00:24:21.541 --> 00:24:23.333
You're so kind! Ha ha ha ha.

466
00:24:23.416 --> 00:24:26.291
Okay. Now say hi to the viewers.

467
00:24:27.000 --> 00:24:29.375
[students] Whoa…

468
00:24:29.458 --> 00:24:30.708
-Uh. hello.
-[Shimura] Hello.

469
00:24:30.791 --> 00:24:32.958
[both] For all of this trouble.
we're so sorry.

470
00:24:33.041 --> 00:24:34.958
Okay. okay. okay then. You hear that?

471
00:24:35.041 --> 00:24:37.166
They've patched things up
between each other now.

472
00:24:37.250 --> 00:24:38.750
and once again. they're best friends.

473
00:24:38.833 --> 00:24:41.875
So you see. you can all relax again. Hmm?

474
00:24:42.333 --> 00:24:45.750
So. how about this?
Today. to celebrate their reconciliation.

475
00:24:45.833 --> 00:24:49.166
we've decided we will be giving away
a brand-new computer

476
00:24:49.250 --> 00:24:52.041
to one lucky viewer out there
who subscribes and likes!

477
00:24:52.125 --> 00:24:54.583
It's a lie! He's lying to you!

478
00:24:54.666 --> 00:24:56.250
-There's no giveaways!
-[boy 2] Hey! Whoa!

479
00:24:56.333 --> 00:24:59.041
There's no way
that he's ever gonna give away a computer!

480
00:24:59.125 --> 00:25:01.750
[tense electronic music playing]

481
00:25:01.833 --> 00:25:03.958
You must know Hamaken is a fraud.

482
00:25:04.041 --> 00:25:04.958
What?

483
00:25:05.041 --> 00:25:07.666
All those giveaways are lies.

484
00:25:07.750 --> 00:25:09.958
It gets him more subscribers. you see?

485
00:25:10.041 --> 00:25:12.125
But he's never given anything away.

486
00:25:12.208 --> 00:25:14.500
Hamaken. he's a filthy fraud!

487
00:25:15.125 --> 00:25:18.291
He said he'd pay me 1.000 yen
for my last appearance!

488
00:25:18.375 --> 00:25:19.791
Let's expose him.

489
00:25:20.458 --> 00:25:22.083
And then everyone will know!

490
00:25:22.166 --> 00:25:23.833
He acts like a good guy on camera.

491
00:25:23.916 --> 00:25:26.750
but behind the scenes.
he beats up on everyone!

492
00:25:26.833 --> 00:25:30.541
-He's just a good-for-nothing delinquent!
-What the hell are you saying?

493
00:25:30.625 --> 00:25:33.833
Have a look at this!
Hamaken did this to me!

494
00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:39.333
Ha!

495
00:25:39.416 --> 00:25:43.541
[forced laughter]

496
00:25:43.625 --> 00:25:45.250
You idiot.

497
00:25:45.750 --> 00:25:48.083
We stopped streaming a while ago.

498
00:25:52.041 --> 00:25:54.750
So who were you calling a fraud?

499
00:25:54.833 --> 00:25:56.375
[yelps]

500
00:25:56.458 --> 00:25:57.541
[boy 3] Whoa!

501
00:25:57.625 --> 00:25:58.500
[Hamaken] Look.

502
00:25:59.416 --> 00:26:01.500
-[Shimura gasping]
-[Hamaken grunting]

503
00:26:01.583 --> 00:26:02.708
[students murmuring]

504
00:26:02.791 --> 00:26:04.125
-[grunts]
-[students yell]

505
00:26:05.208 --> 00:26:06.041
[groaning] Agh!

506
00:26:06.125 --> 00:26:08.208
[boy 4] Hamaken! Hamaken!
Let's go! Go! Let's go!

507
00:26:08.291 --> 00:26:10.791
-[students chattering]
-[girl 1] Oh. man. Hamaken's pissed.

508
00:26:11.666 --> 00:26:13.166
Were you trying to expose me?

509
00:26:13.250 --> 00:26:15.416
-Were you trying to take revenge?
-[Shimura groaning]

510
00:26:15.500 --> 00:26:17.291
-[grunts] Ah!
-[students gasp]

511
00:26:17.791 --> 00:26:20.375
-[grunts] Ah! Ah!
-[students gasping]

512
00:26:20.458 --> 00:26:22.083
-[kick thuds]
-[Hamaken grunts] Ah!

513
00:26:22.833 --> 00:26:24.666
-[Hamaken grunting] Ah! Ah!
-[whimpering]

514
00:26:25.916 --> 00:26:26.916
[Shimura] Expose him?

515
00:26:27.541 --> 00:26:28.458
On his channel?

516
00:26:28.541 --> 00:26:32.250
-No. No. We do it on our channel.
-Huh?

517
00:26:32.333 --> 00:26:34.666
Right now.
you and I are minor celebrities.

518
00:26:34.750 --> 00:26:36.791
This exposé video will go viral.

519
00:26:36.875 --> 00:26:39.958
[dramatic music playing]

520
00:26:40.041 --> 00:26:40.875
No!

521
00:26:40.958 --> 00:26:43.333
-If I do that. he'll beat me up again.
-Money.

522
00:26:45.541 --> 00:26:46.958
Don't you want money?

523
00:26:49.541 --> 00:26:52.500
[sighs] I guess I have no other choice.

524
00:26:54.416 --> 00:26:57.041
If we succeed in exposing him.

525
00:26:57.125 --> 00:26:58.833
I'll give you 10.000 yen.

526
00:26:58.916 --> 00:27:00.583
[Hamaken kicks] Get up! You hear me?

527
00:27:00.666 --> 00:27:02.166
I said get up!

528
00:27:02.250 --> 00:27:03.708
[boy 1] Hey. wanna go see Hamaken?

529
00:27:03.791 --> 00:27:06.125
[girl 1] Who picked a fight?
This is crazy!

530
00:27:06.208 --> 00:27:08.875
[girl 2] Who'd pick a fight with Hamaken?
Are they insane?

531
00:27:08.958 --> 00:27:10.958
-[Hamaken roars]
-[girls shriek]

532
00:27:11.041 --> 00:27:12.208
[Shimura groans]

533
00:27:12.291 --> 00:27:14.833
[gasping. sobbing]

534
00:27:14.916 --> 00:27:17.333
Don't you ever mess
with me again. you hear?

535
00:27:17.416 --> 00:27:19.416
[Shimura crying]

536
00:27:20.875 --> 00:27:23.208
-[dramatic music playing]
-[Hamaken] Huh?

537
00:27:24.500 --> 00:27:25.625
Money.

538
00:27:27.750 --> 00:27:30.750
You owe me… 1.000 yen.

539
00:27:31.583 --> 00:27:32.708
What the hell's up with you?

540
00:27:33.458 --> 00:27:34.333
[boy 2 laughs]

541
00:27:34.416 --> 00:27:35.500
[Hamaken] Hmm?

542
00:27:36.041 --> 00:27:38.708
You want me to beat you to a pulp? Do you?

543
00:27:39.291 --> 00:27:42.125
Fine by me. you piece of shit.

544
00:27:42.708 --> 00:27:44.666
[boy 3] Who's causing the ruckus?

545
00:27:54.208 --> 00:27:55.041
Is it you?

546
00:27:56.166 --> 00:27:57.041
No.

547
00:27:57.666 --> 00:27:59.083
Will you keep it down?

548
00:27:59.166 --> 00:28:00.000
I can't nap.

549
00:28:01.666 --> 00:28:03.250
Oh. All right.

550
00:28:08.291 --> 00:28:10.833
[students murmuring]

551
00:28:12.458 --> 00:28:13.291
Hey.

552
00:28:14.833 --> 00:28:15.708
Hey!

553
00:28:24.291 --> 00:28:25.958
[groans] It hurts.

554
00:28:27.083 --> 00:28:28.541
Hey. you're alive.

555
00:28:30.041 --> 00:28:32.125
Uh. how did I get here?

556
00:28:32.208 --> 00:28:34.000
It was Ogi from the class next door.

557
00:28:35.916 --> 00:28:37.166
Ogi?

558
00:28:39.250 --> 00:28:41.208
[boy] Ogi Tatsuya.

559
00:28:41.291 --> 00:28:44.791
A man who exists
outside of the school's social ladder.

560
00:28:44.875 --> 00:28:48.791
A high schooler and rising star
in the world of MMA fighting.

561
00:28:48.875 --> 00:28:52.333
So. what happened? The exposé video?

562
00:28:54.791 --> 00:28:56.708
[Hamaken on video] You trying
to take revenge?

563
00:28:56.791 --> 00:28:59.000
-[Hamaken grunts] Ah!
-[students gasp]

564
00:28:59.083 --> 00:29:00.041
[Hamaken grunts] Ah!

565
00:29:02.125 --> 00:29:03.625
It's gone viral!

566
00:29:03.708 --> 00:29:06.166
Yeah. It was a success!

567
00:29:06.250 --> 00:29:07.583
Yes! You owe me 10.000--

568
00:29:07.666 --> 00:29:09.208
Sorry. I can't give it to you.

569
00:29:09.291 --> 00:29:11.916
Huh? Why not? We made a deal.

570
00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:14.875
You didn't last long enough.
That's your problem.

571
00:29:14.958 --> 00:29:15.916
What?

572
00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:19.125
Short videos. you see.
they don't make enough money.

573
00:29:19.208 --> 00:29:21.333
There's just not enough ad revenue.

574
00:29:21.750 --> 00:29:25.125
That's why we've gotta go after donations.

575
00:29:25.833 --> 00:29:26.875
Donations.

576
00:29:26.958 --> 00:29:30.541
Even with donations.
long videos still rake in more money.

577
00:29:30.625 --> 00:29:33.666
And even long videos.
you still don't get the full amount.

578
00:29:33.750 --> 00:29:37.458
After all the fees.
there's still only about 60 percent left.

579
00:29:37.541 --> 00:29:40.041
In this case.

580
00:29:40.125 --> 00:29:41.208
3.900.

581
00:29:41.291 --> 00:29:43.625
3.900?! After all that effort?

582
00:29:43.708 --> 00:29:45.791
That's what happens
when the video's short.

583
00:29:45.875 --> 00:29:48.291
And it doesn't help
that we don't have many followers yet.

584
00:29:48.375 --> 00:29:50.166
I had no idea.

585
00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:54.458
Hey. Hold on a sec.

586
00:29:54.541 --> 00:29:57.250
None of this is any of my problem.
You should pay what you promised--

587
00:29:57.333 --> 00:29:58.708
Okay. right now

588
00:29:59.375 --> 00:30:02.541
I'm asking if you're happy settling
for a measly 10.000.

589
00:30:04.125 --> 00:30:06.708
This video has already reached
one million views.

590
00:30:06.791 --> 00:30:08.708
As the views increase.
so will the followers.

591
00:30:08.791 --> 00:30:12.916
If we can stream for longer.
making millions won't be a dream!

592
00:30:17.875 --> 00:30:19.083
Did you know

593
00:30:19.583 --> 00:30:23.333
that sometimes from a single stream
you can make over 200 million?

594
00:30:23.416 --> 00:30:25.833
-200?!
-Million!

595
00:30:26.375 --> 00:30:27.916
200 million.

596
00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.458
It's up to you.

597
00:30:32.166 --> 00:30:33.041
Hey.

598
00:30:35.458 --> 00:30:36.291
Hey. Shimura?

599
00:30:38.250 --> 00:30:39.458
Did you get any of that?

600
00:30:39.541 --> 00:30:41.833
Oh. Uh. sorry.

601
00:30:42.583 --> 00:30:44.541
What's wrong with you? Little creep.

602
00:30:47.375 --> 00:30:51.541
So. if... if we did a live stream.
what would we do?

603
00:30:55.583 --> 00:30:57.500
[militant rock music playing]

604
00:30:57.583 --> 00:30:58.875
Fights?

605
00:30:58.958 --> 00:31:02.916
-Yeah. Our main content will be fighting.
-Wait a minute.

606
00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:05.041
Picking fights
with delinquents in real time.

607
00:31:05.125 --> 00:31:06.333
But videos of fights are--

608
00:31:06.416 --> 00:31:09.291
It's about the idea.
Striking gold isn't easy.

609
00:31:09.375 --> 00:31:10.375
You have a point. but…

610
00:31:10.458 --> 00:31:12.708
I'm convinced by our recent success.

611
00:31:12.791 --> 00:31:16.500
It went viral because the underdog
picked a fight with a bully

612
00:31:17.000 --> 00:31:18.041
[Shimura] You owe me

613
00:31:18.958 --> 00:31:20.583
1.000 yen.

614
00:31:24.625 --> 00:31:26.041
Let's team up.

615
00:31:26.791 --> 00:31:30.083
-Huh?
-Starting today. I'm your producer. okay?

616
00:31:30.166 --> 00:31:33.250
With our next video.
we'll rake in the donations.

617
00:31:34.375 --> 00:31:37.291
Let's take over the world
with this channel.

618
00:31:37.375 --> 00:31:39.375
[rock music continues]

619
00:31:41.708 --> 00:31:42.833
[grunts]

620
00:31:43.500 --> 00:31:45.708
I'll have you rolling in cash.

621
00:31:50.083 --> 00:31:51.083
Rolling in cash?

622
00:31:55.375 --> 00:31:56.500
So we're set.

623
00:31:57.208 --> 00:32:01.125
I need you to be able to drag out a fight
and make it last no matter what.

624
00:32:10.791 --> 00:32:13.458
-[camera clicking]
-[giggles]

625
00:32:14.041 --> 00:32:16.083
So good. Totally insta-worthy.

626
00:32:16.166 --> 00:32:19.333
-[Hamaken groaning]
-How much longer are you going to take?

627
00:32:19.416 --> 00:32:20.750
-[Rumi] Oh.
-[camera clicking]

628
00:32:21.250 --> 00:32:25.708
Oh… but… Hey. Hey.

629
00:32:26.750 --> 00:32:29.166
You take our time.

630
00:32:29.250 --> 00:32:33.041
Can't we get on with it?
Baby. don't drag it out.

631
00:32:33.541 --> 00:32:34.375
[Yumi] Huh?

632
00:32:36.583 --> 00:32:37.708
What this?

633
00:32:38.666 --> 00:32:40.083
[grunting on video]

634
00:32:41.541 --> 00:32:43.708
-[snarling]
-[Hamaken on video] Get up.

635
00:32:43.791 --> 00:32:45.916
Those shitheads! God damn!

636
00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:48.583
POPULAR STREAMER HAMAKEN
IS A TEENAGE DELINQUENT!

637
00:32:51.625 --> 00:32:53.875
[grunting and thudding on video]

638
00:32:55.750 --> 00:32:58.416
How to last in a fight. huh?

639
00:32:59.000 --> 00:32:59.875
[gasps]

640
00:33:00.875 --> 00:33:02.500
[grunting on video continues]

641
00:33:04.375 --> 00:33:05.333
[mouse clicks]

642
00:33:06.458 --> 00:33:07.625
[funky music playing]

643
00:33:07.708 --> 00:33:09.958
HOW TO FIGHT BETTER

644
00:33:12.750 --> 00:33:15.791
STRENGTH TRAINING
TO IMPROVE FIGHTING

645
00:33:16.875 --> 00:33:17.750
[clicking]

646
00:33:17.833 --> 00:33:19.500
GET STRONGER
WITH MARTIAL ARTS

647
00:33:19.583 --> 00:33:20.875
I should've expected this.

648
00:33:20.958 --> 00:33:22.000
JOIN A MARTIAL ARTS GYM

649
00:33:22.083 --> 00:33:23.916
BOXING VIDEO

650
00:33:24.000 --> 00:33:24.875
[mouse clicks]

651
00:33:30.083 --> 00:33:33.666
I think I'd die… if I did this.

652
00:33:33.750 --> 00:33:35.250
[man on video] Yeah. that's it.

653
00:33:35.333 --> 00:33:38.125
-[Hamaken yelling indistinctly on video]
-I'm not cut out for this.

654
00:33:38.625 --> 00:33:41.583
Besides. why am I the one
who has to get beaten?

655
00:33:41.666 --> 00:33:43.375
This is so crazy.

656
00:33:45.458 --> 00:33:46.875
YOU'RE BRAVE. SHIMURA

657
00:33:49.250 --> 00:33:52.375
"How_to_fight"? Mm.

658
00:33:53.250 --> 00:33:54.458
-What's this?
-[clicks]

659
00:33:59.416 --> 00:34:00.708
Zero.

660
00:34:00.791 --> 00:34:02.708
Doesn't have any views?

661
00:34:15.375 --> 00:34:17.375
FIGHTING MINDSET
0 VIEWS

662
00:34:22.750 --> 00:34:24.250
[clicking]

663
00:34:33.708 --> 00:34:35.708
[ominous music playing]

664
00:34:44.416 --> 00:34:46.416
[dramatic percussive sounds echoing]

665
00:34:48.416 --> 00:34:49.375
TOU-KEI

666
00:34:53.750 --> 00:34:57.833
Hello guys. My name is TOU-KEI.

667
00:34:57.916 --> 00:35:00.458
Why don't you come
and get stronger with me?

668
00:35:00.541 --> 00:35:02.916
-Why is he a chicken?
-[jaunty pop music playing]

669
00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.125
Want to know how to get stronger?

670
00:35:05.208 --> 00:35:07.250
It's really very easy.

671
00:35:07.333 --> 00:35:09.750
Just become my friend.
That's all you need to do.

672
00:35:09.833 --> 00:35:11.208
Is he not Japanese?

673
00:35:11.291 --> 00:35:15.666
I can teach you how to become strong.
everything you need to know step-by-step.

674
00:35:16.666 --> 00:35:20.208
Did you know when it comes
to winning a fight. there's a secret?

675
00:35:20.291 --> 00:35:21.166
Huh?

676
00:35:21.250 --> 00:35:25.750
And if you're interested.
I can teach you what that secret is.

677
00:35:25.833 --> 00:35:27.125
-But first…
-Seriously?

678
00:35:27.208 --> 00:35:29.833
…let's talk about the fighting mindset.

679
00:35:29.916 --> 00:35:32.083
-Now. step one…
-[mouse clicks]

680
00:35:35.166 --> 00:35:38.000
I think this guy is nuts.

681
00:35:39.291 --> 00:35:41.208
I can't do this.

682
00:35:41.875 --> 00:35:43.791
Hello there. I'm Hamaken.

683
00:35:43.875 --> 00:35:48.000
Today. I'm gonna ask girls enjoying
the nightlife about their dark past.

684
00:35:48.833 --> 00:35:50.666
Hey. ladies. Ladies. Hey. ladies.

685
00:35:50.750 --> 00:35:52.708
Can you tell me about things
in your dark past?

686
00:35:52.791 --> 00:35:54.958
-Hamaken. ew!
-You've got to be kidding me!

687
00:35:55.041 --> 00:35:56.708
Don't be like that.
Tell me something saucy!

688
00:35:56.791 --> 00:35:57.791
HOW'S THE BACKLASH?
THE AUDACITY!

689
00:35:57.875 --> 00:36:00.333
-Don't film us without permission!
-Creepy loser!

690
00:36:00.416 --> 00:36:02.416
[din of music and chattering]

691
00:36:06.250 --> 00:36:08.333
-[dance music playing]
-[Hamaken] Not feeling it today.

692
00:36:08.416 --> 00:36:09.708
Time for a break.

693
00:36:12.041 --> 00:36:13.291
Hey! No high schoolers allowed.

694
00:36:13.375 --> 00:36:14.500
What? You always let me in.

695
00:36:14.583 --> 00:36:17.750
-No.
-Hey! Let go of me! Let go! Hey!

696
00:36:17.833 --> 00:36:19.708
I want to see the manager. Hey!

697
00:36:19.791 --> 00:36:21.375
Hey! Rumi!

698
00:36:21.458 --> 00:36:23.250
-Good work.
-Hey. Rumi!

699
00:36:23.333 --> 00:36:25.583
Hey! Hey! Take your hands off me!

700
00:36:25.666 --> 00:36:27.291
Let me go! Let go!

701
00:36:28.375 --> 00:36:29.291
[music stops]

702
00:36:36.083 --> 00:36:37.208
[sighs]

703
00:36:43.541 --> 00:36:47.166
[Hamaken] You've got to ask yourself.
is your mother still alive? Is she?

704
00:36:47.250 --> 00:36:48.500
[tense music playing]

705
00:36:48.583 --> 00:36:51.625
I suggested it to your mother.
but she declined.

706
00:36:53.583 --> 00:36:56.041
I'll have you rolling in cash.

707
00:36:59.916 --> 00:37:00.833
[music ends]

708
00:37:00.916 --> 00:37:02.583
[screams]

709
00:37:02.666 --> 00:37:05.083
[TOU-KEI] Don't you get lonely
being by yourself?

710
00:37:05.166 --> 00:37:08.208
-Why are you here?!
-Don't you want to become stronger?

711
00:37:08.708 --> 00:37:12.000
If you'll be my friend.
then you can get stronger with me.

712
00:37:12.083 --> 00:37:13.083
What the hell?

713
00:37:13.166 --> 00:37:15.875
[TOU-KEI] Become stronger.
and you can change your world!

714
00:37:15.958 --> 00:37:18.375
Get lost! Go! [grunts]

715
00:37:19.458 --> 00:37:21.500
[gasping]

716
00:37:22.625 --> 00:37:25.500
[gasping]

717
00:37:28.666 --> 00:37:30.250
-[thud on video]
-[Hamaken on video] Huh?

718
00:37:31.375 --> 00:37:32.708
[Shimura] Money.

719
00:37:34.208 --> 00:37:37.833
You owe me… 1.000 yen.

720
00:37:39.250 --> 00:37:40.791
[Hamaken] What the hell's up with you?

721
00:37:41.916 --> 00:37:44.375
You want me
to beat you to a pulp. do you?

722
00:37:45.583 --> 00:37:48.750
Fine by me. you piece of shit.

723
00:37:53.500 --> 00:37:55.500
[students chattering indistinctly]

724
00:38:15.375 --> 00:38:16.708
Hey! Get outta my way!

725
00:38:18.875 --> 00:38:20.916
Oh. Shimura! This is bad.  Really bad.

726
00:38:21.000 --> 00:38:21.916
-[roars]
-Oh. yeah!

727
00:38:22.000 --> 00:38:22.833
Hey!

728
00:38:22.916 --> 00:38:25.541
-Come with me! Hurry!
-[boy 1] And him too!

729
00:38:25.625 --> 00:38:27.666
[gasping] Let's go that way.

730
00:38:27.750 --> 00:38:30.208
[Hamaken roars] Ah!
Where the hell do you think you're going?

731
00:38:30.291 --> 00:38:31.291
[barks] Ah!

732
00:38:31.375 --> 00:38:34.291
-[Shimura whimpering]
-You're dead! You're fucking dead!

733
00:38:34.375 --> 00:38:37.875
[Shimura yelling. screaming]

734
00:38:37.958 --> 00:38:38.791
[boy 1] Move it!

735
00:38:38.875 --> 00:38:41.041
-[boy 3] Hey! Hey!  It's a fight!
-[boy 4] Huh?

736
00:38:41.125 --> 00:38:44.500
-Who's fighting?
-[boy 3] Hamaken. He's super pissed!

737
00:38:46.458 --> 00:38:48.625
-[Hamaken grunting] Agh! Agh!
-[Shimura gasping]

738
00:38:48.708 --> 00:38:50.791
-[Shimura grunting]
-[girls shriek]

739
00:38:52.791 --> 00:38:54.708
[boy 1] I say it was an accident.

740
00:38:54.791 --> 00:38:55.666
[laughing]

741
00:38:55.750 --> 00:38:58.166
-You think you're so tough? Huh?!
-Whoa-ho-ho!

742
00:38:58.250 --> 00:39:00.208
-But you're not. So take this!
-[Shimura grunting]

743
00:39:00.291 --> 00:39:01.583
[boys] Whoa-ho!

744
00:39:01.666 --> 00:39:03.708
-[boys laughing]
-[Hamaken] There. now!

745
00:39:03.791 --> 00:39:06.333
Die! Die! You little shit!

746
00:39:07.041 --> 00:39:09.916
You! Bastard! You bastard!
You're gonna die!

747
00:39:10.000 --> 00:39:11.583
[boy 4] Stop it. Hamaken!

748
00:39:11.666 --> 00:39:13.791
[tense rock music playing]

749
00:39:14.625 --> 00:39:16.666
Everyone's going to see this.

750
00:39:17.625 --> 00:39:19.791
You think so? I doubt that.

751
00:39:19.875 --> 00:39:20.875
Huh?

752
00:39:20.958 --> 00:39:21.875
Oh. yeah!

753
00:39:21.958 --> 00:39:25.250
[boys grunting]

754
00:39:26.416 --> 00:39:27.583
[boy 4 groaning]

755
00:39:32.875 --> 00:39:34.625
-[grunting]
-[boys laughing]

756
00:39:34.708 --> 00:39:37.375
I'll make sure you never defy me again.

757
00:39:37.458 --> 00:39:38.458
You hear me? Huh?!

758
00:39:38.541 --> 00:39:41.041
-[girls scream]
-[boy 2] Hey! Don't run away!

759
00:39:41.125 --> 00:39:42.791
-Don't run away! Hey!
-[Shimura] Agh!

760
00:39:42.875 --> 00:39:45.958
[Hamaken snarls] You are a piece of trash!

761
00:39:46.041 --> 00:39:47.375
-[Shimura groans]
-[Hamaken] Yeah!

762
00:39:47.458 --> 00:39:49.291
-This is just for starters!
-[boy 1] Hey.  Hey!

763
00:39:49.375 --> 00:39:51.083
[boy 2] Uh-uh! No running away!

764
00:39:51.166 --> 00:39:54.958
-You're nothing but a lowlife!
-[students scream]

765
00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:57.875
[gasping for air]

766
00:39:58.500 --> 00:40:00.750
[Hamaken] Where do you think you're going?

767
00:40:00.833 --> 00:40:04.875
You deserve to spend the rest of your life
crawling on the ground!

768
00:40:05.833 --> 00:40:08.708
[gasping. straining]

769
00:40:08.791 --> 00:40:10.791
[tense music playing]

770
00:40:12.750 --> 00:40:14.041
[Shimura shudders]

771
00:40:14.666 --> 00:40:17.291
[boy 4] Stop it. Don't look over here.

772
00:40:19.708 --> 00:40:21.750
Hey. stop looking at me.

773
00:40:27.541 --> 00:40:29.000
I've got you on camera.

774
00:40:34.708 --> 00:40:35.708
[whispers] Let's go.

775
00:40:37.833 --> 00:40:39.208
Give me your phone!

776
00:40:39.291 --> 00:40:40.375
Huh? What for?

777
00:40:40.458 --> 00:40:41.458
Are you stupid?

778
00:40:41.541 --> 00:40:43.666
We've really got to get smart about this.

779
00:40:43.750 --> 00:40:46.000
Now listen very carefully.

780
00:40:46.500 --> 00:40:48.750
They're going to take
my phone away from me.

781
00:40:48.833 --> 00:40:49.916
-Huh?
-So let's get smart!

782
00:40:50.000 --> 00:40:51.750
Hang on. I don't understand. What is--

783
00:40:51.833 --> 00:40:53.583
I'm saying this is our chance.

784
00:40:54.458 --> 00:40:55.583
Our chance?

785
00:40:56.500 --> 00:40:58.583
Yeah. To make a killing.

786
00:41:03.833 --> 00:41:04.750
Hey.

787
00:41:04.833 --> 00:41:07.458
You keep your head down now. you hear me?

788
00:41:09.833 --> 00:41:10.666
[huffs]

789
00:41:10.750 --> 00:41:13.500
[footsteps departing]

790
00:41:16.250 --> 00:41:18.625
[straining. gasping]

791
00:41:20.791 --> 00:41:22.833
[tense music swells]

792
00:41:22.916 --> 00:41:23.875
[groans]

793
00:41:23.958 --> 00:41:26.583
[Shimura] Being on top
never really mattered to me.

794
00:41:31.166 --> 00:41:32.375
All I need…

795
00:41:33.625 --> 00:41:34.791
is money.

796
00:41:35.291 --> 00:41:36.666
[Shimura gasping]

797
00:41:38.541 --> 00:41:40.750
The underdog bites back at the bully.

798
00:41:42.041 --> 00:41:44.416
That's what's gonna make us rich. right?

799
00:41:49.916 --> 00:41:51.958
[shuddering]

800
00:41:52.041 --> 00:41:54.416
[breathing deeply]

801
00:41:59.083 --> 00:42:00.041
VIEWS: 1

802
00:42:04.375 --> 00:42:06.375
[tense music intensifying]

803
00:42:27.625 --> 00:42:29.708
Go on. Come at me.

804
00:42:30.375 --> 00:42:32.333
You piece of shit.

805
00:42:35.291 --> 00:42:37.958
[rock music in Japanese playing]

806
00:42:47.125 --> 00:42:53.375
VIRAL HIT

807
00:42:59.333 --> 00:43:01.375
[rock music in Japanese continues]

808
00:44:10.791 --> 00:44:11.750
[music ends]
